text:
On URL:
http://httpd.apache.org/docs-2.0/vhosts/
(or http://httpd.apache.org/docs-2.0/vhosts/index.html.en if another language is
set on your browser)

There's a table on the right "See Also" which last link is called "Detalis of
host matching".
Should be "Details of host matching".

Also in current CVS:
http://cvs.apache.org/viewcvs.cgi/httpd-docs-2.0/manual/vhosts/index.html.en
Fixed, thanks for reporting the issue and using Apache 2.0!
